    <h2 {...{
      "id": "create-a-configuration-file-and-tests"
    }}>{`Create a Configuration File and Tests`}</h2>
    <p>{`If you're starting your journey without tests, follow the steps below in order to generate a config file, which in turn creates the necessary test files in your project's root directory.`}</p>
