    <h3 {...{
      "id": "authenticate"
    }}>{`Authenticate`}</h3>
    <p>{`To get started, you must: `}<a parentName="p" {...{
        "href": "/testrunner-toolkit/installation"
      }}>{`download and install testrunner toolkit`}</a>{` and run the following command to authenticate Sauce Labs:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-bash"
      }}>{`saucectl configure
`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`The command then generates a `}<inlineCode parentName="p">{`credentials.yml`}</inlineCode>{` file:`}</p>
    <pre><code parentName="pre" {...{
        "className": "language-yaml",
        "metastring": "title=\"example cypress credentials.yml\"",
        "title": "\"example",
        "cypress": true,
        "credentials.yml\"": true
      }}>{`username: <your saucelabs username>
accessKey: xxxxxxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxx-xxxxxxxxxxxx
source: environment variables
`}</code></pre>
    <div {...{
      "className": "admonition admonition-warning alert alert--danger"
    }}><div parentName="div" {...{
